             was indicted for that he <rs id="t17770115-34-off168" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17770115-34-off168" type="offenceCategory" value="violentTheft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17770115-34-off168" type="offenceSubcategory" value="highwayRobbery"></interp>
               in the king's highway in and upon 
                     <persName id="t17770115-34-person363">
                        John
                         Edgely
                     <interp inst="t17770115-34-person363" type="surname" value="Edgely"></interp>
