                        <interp inst="t17770115-34-person363" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                   did make an assault, putting him in corporal fear and danger of his life, and stealing from his person one bank post bill, marked X. No 6260, dated London, 13th May 1776, signed by 
                     <persName id="t17770115-34-person364">
                        John
                         Boult
                     <interp inst="t17770115-34-person364" type="surname" value="Boult"></interp>
