                  , for the governor and company of the Bank of England, by which the said John at 7 days sight did promise to pay that his solar bill of exchange to Mr. 
                     <persName id="t17770115-34-person365">
                        Graham
                         Wilkinson
                     <interp inst="t17770115-34-person365" type="surname" value="Wilkinson"></interp>
